{"tid":1738027,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[和理非戰略] 民意分析及文宣方向","createTime":"2019-11-19T06:20:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T19:57:36.000Z","uid":254381,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"40690a5e6f1e2e6f4171729d963ea4bca9bcbef5","tid":1738027,"uid":254381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:20:41.000Z","msg":"其實一見到個民調就想做呢樣野，但望到 poly 嘅手足咁實在無 mood。而家情況明朗翻啲，希望和理非們一齊諗諗呢個 post 嘅野。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最近喺隔籬 post 見到鍾庭耀教授做咗個民調 (<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1</a>) ，好似幾信得過咁，所以小弟用咗粒幾鐘睇，大概 spot到以下嘅 takeaways:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">黃：好贊成 / 贊成</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">藍：好反對 / 反對</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">綠：唔知 / 中立</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>大方向：</strong><br />\n1. 我地<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>贏緊民意</strong></span>！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（15日內 多左<span style=\"color: gold;\">10%</span> 黃、少左<span style=\"color: blue;\">10%</span> 藍）<br />\n2. 藍綠民意<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>浮動潛力大</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（問卷陣營SD：黃<span style=\"color: gold;\"> 18%</span>｜綠 <span style=\"color: green;\">36%</span>｜藍 <span style=\"color: blue;\">33%</span>）<br />\n3. 各陣營細節普遍沒有共識<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （問卷細項SD：<span style=\"color: gold;\">~30%</span> 好贊成/幾贊成｜<span style=\"color: green;\">~50%</span> 中立/唔知｜<span style=\"color: blue;\">~40%</span> 好反對/幾反對）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>黃：</strong></span><br />\n4. 可改善：黃絲都<span style=\"color: red;\">要翻工</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（不合作運動：<span style=\"color: gold;\">21%</span> 好贊成 vs 好贊成平均 <span style=\"color: gold;\">47%</span>）<br />\n5. 可改善：<span style=\"color: red;\">黃色經濟圈</span>要人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（杯葛或支持個別品牌：<span style=\"color: green;\">20%</span> 中立/唔知）<br />\n6. 重 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Fact check</span></strong> 精神：無鐵證就唔會確信<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（新屋嶺有性侵：<span style=\"color: gold;\">35%</span> 好贊成 &amp; <span style=\"color: green;\">14%</span> 唔知｜8.31 有打死人：<span style=\"color: gold;\">31%</span> 好贊成 &amp; <span style=\"color: green;\">14%</span> 唔知｜vs 平均：<span style=\"color: gold;\">47%</span> 好贊成 &amp; <span style=\"color: green;\">7%</span> 唔知）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>藍：</strong></span><br />\n7. 可改變：一半藍絲<span style=\"color: red;\">無血性</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（彥霖死因聆訊：<span style=\"color: blue;\">12%</span> 藍｜獨立調查7.21：<span style=\"color: blue;\">14%</span> 藍）｜<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一半藍絲有血性</span></strong> （平均：<span style=\"color: blue;\">22%</span> 藍）<br />\n8. <span style=\"color: red;\">自私</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（不合作運動：<span style=\"color: blue;\">30%</span> 好反對）<br />\n9. 對<span style=\"color: red;\">外國界入</span>敏感<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（<span style=\"color: blue;\">23%</span> 好反對《人權法案》，但幾反對得 6%）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">綠：</span><br />\n10. 大部分<span style=\"color: red;\">牆頭草</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（<span style=\"color: green;\">綠SD</span>為平均值一平）<br />\n11. 中立：有<span style=\"color: red;\">道德批判</span>能力 / 左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（清真寺道歉：<span style=\"color: green;\">2%</span> 一半半｜7.21 停職涉嫌警員：<span style=\"color: green;\">2%</span> 一半半｜8.31 傷者提出民事訴頌：<span style=\"color: green;\">3%</span> 一半半）<br />\n12. 唔知：事不關己，己不勞心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（取消功能組別：<span style=\"color: green;\">15%</span> 唔知｜不合作運作： <span style=\"color: green;\">2% </span>唔知）<br />\n<br />\n重點：<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>民意無輸，但都唔係完全唔洗理</strong></span>，對象係自己人嘅文宣要<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">注意邏輯證據</span></strong>、切忌9 up；同手足切忌喺細節過份斟酌，大家要記得共同目的，乜都有得傾，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好比人分化</span></strong>。方向嚟講，要加強不合作運動同黃色生態圈嘅宣傳。<br />\n2. 要感化綠絲係要<span style=\"color: red;\">小心佢地嘅左膠原則</span>，同令佢地覺得佢地係關事嘅。<br />\n3. 要感化藍絲就更加要技有巧避開無辦法打得贏佢嘅位，要運用<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">高階策略</span></strong>，例如各種謬論、針對攻擊時喺某啲位讓步等等。<br />\n<br />\n頭盔：民調嘅問題設計、population等等可能令到以上分析有bias，請各位文宣手足自行判斷、啱用拎去；最後一份民調公佈日期為十一月十六日。<br />\n<br />\n呢場喺一場長期抗爭，要贏，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一定要有更多更多嘅同伴</span></strong>。與其將局面絕對二元分化、唔係撐我地就係敵人，不如落多啲心機、多啲包容，感化多啲人企喺我地果邊。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而感化藍絲技巧方面的確有唔少鑽研嘅空間，而家都有唔少手足做緊呢方面嘅文宣，我下一篇文就會嘗試拆解下點樣將訊息狠狠咁塞入藍絲個腦。手足身邊有藍絲不妨試下搵下佢地做實驗，一齊交流下佢地嘅feedback，同一齊分享下心得，等小弟略盡綿力，分析下，試下部署大舉進攻藍營！！！<br />\n<br />\n香港人，進化！"},{"pid":"fe908160ce4b063766ee0fae7f1bc17f6e6758cb","tid":1738027,"uid":338636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:21:42.000Z","msg":"[正能量撚]出去之前，希望你可以睇下呢個po<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1734559\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1734559</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>全個連登都係負能量，我要你地有正能量啊</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"539b9355b6d568c0d5412422b45d551755d9f875","tid":1738027,"uid":254381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:31:05.000Z","msg":"推到全部和理非都見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img sr